articles.author: Peter Valdes-Dapena
articles.title: GM to stop making Chevy Camaro, leaving muscle car's future uncertain - CNN
articles.description: General Motors announced Wednesday that it's ending production of the latest generation of the Chevrolet Camaro, leaving the Ford Mustang as the last gasoline-powered American performance coupe.
